Package malp.DemonSkies

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DemonSkiesGame
    The class representing the resulting game and containing the DemonSkiesGame.main(String[]) entry point.
    GameEngine
    The GameEngine represents the current game state, including the Player entity, enemy entities, and statistics such as the GameEngine.score, GameEngine.highScore, and GameEngine.souls.
    ResourceManager
    The ResourceManager is responsible for loading in all resources used by other objects and then providing them to conserve memory.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    UpgradeType
    The Enum UpgradeType represents the player upgrades available.
